<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>1375</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 bāng zhù wǒ men de shì wàn jūn zhī yé hé huá, jiù shì chuàng zào tiān de wàn yǒu de yé hé huá,
 tā zhǔ zǎi lì shǐ tǒng guǎn pǔ tiān xià, zài wú bié shén néng xiàng tā,
 wú lùn zǒu dào hǎi jiǎo tiān yá, yǒu zhǔ tóng zài jiù shì jiā,
 gāo jǔ zhǔ shèng míng qián jìn bù jù pà, fú yīn yǐ zài gè chù kāi huā,
 hā lì lù yà zàn měi yé hé huá, wàn guó wàn mín dōu yào jìng bài tā,
 yé hé huá zài quán de wèi dà zài quán de zuì dà, tā yǐ jīng bǎ chóu dí dǎ kuǎ.</lyrics>
<title>bāng zhù wǒ men de shì wàn jūn zhī yé hé huá 迦南1375</title>
</song>